OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784758688
OL,3,CSpain temperatures to surpass 44C as
OL,4,Cwildfires burn across Europe
OL,6,FSpain is set to see scorching
OL,7,Ftemperatures of more than 44C this
OL,8,Fweek as wildfires continue to burn
OL,9,Facross Europe.
OL,11,FDangerous severe red heat alerts are
OL,12,Fin place in several regions on the
OL,13,Fsouth east coast on Thursday as a
OL,14,Fheatwave sweeps across Europe once
OL,15,Fmore.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
