OL,3,CSpain temperatures to surpass 44C as
OL,4,Cwildfires burn across Europe
OL,6,FVega del Segura and Valle del
OL,7,FGuadalentin, Lorca and Aguilas will
OL,8,Fsee temperatures hotter than 44C,
OL,9,Faccording to Spanish weather
OL,10,Fforecaster Agencia Estatal de
OL,11,FMeteorlogia (AEMET).
OL,13,FFirefighters continue to tackle
OL,14,FSpain's second largest wildfire in
OL,15,Fhistory in Guadalajara, central Spain,
OL,16,Fwhich has already burned 32,000
OL,17,Fhectares of land (around 124 square
OL,18,Fmiles).
