OL,3,CSpain temperatures to surpass 44C as
OL,4,Cwildfires burn across Europe
OL,6,FSo far 34 villages have been evacuated
OL,7,Fand helicopters have been dropping
OL,8,Fwater on the blaze.
OL,10,FThere are no reported injuries.
OL,12,FSpanish Prime Minister Pedro Sanchez
OL,13,Fcalled for politicians to work
OL,14,Ftogether to fight climate change as
OL,15,Fthe country has faced 22 major fires
OL,16,Fthis year, four times more than last
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
