FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784758688
OL,3,CSpain temperatures to surpass 44C as
OL,4,Cwildfires burn across Europe
OL,6,FVisiting emergency services in village
OL,7,Fof Tamajon, near the blaze, he
OL,8,Fdescribed how more than 100,000
OL,9,Fhectares (386 square miles) have been
OL,10,Fscorched in Spanish wildfires, which
OL,11,Fis the "annual average that Spain
OL,12,Fsuffered in the last decade".
OL,14,FHe warned: "Year after year we clearly
OL,15,Fsee how climate change kills and
OL,16,Fdestroys wealth in our communities.
OL,17,FThis isn't politics. It is science,
OL,18,Fit's about facts."
OL,26,@oD@IrwzD@RO]
