OL,3,CSpain temperatures to surpass 44C as
OL,4,Cwildfires burn across Europe
OL,6,FIt comes just two weeks after a
OL,7,Fwildfire in southern Spain killed 13
OL,8,Fpeople including seven Brits. On
OL,9,FWednesday, July 22, forecasters
OL,10,Fannounced Spain's third heatwave of
OL,11,Fthe year.
OL,13,FIn Cotignac, southern France, a
OL,14,Ffirefighters worked to extinguish a
OL,15,Fblaze as drought conditions worsen
OL,16,Ffollowing the heatwave.
OL,18,FAcross Italy more than 100 hectares of
OL,19,Fwoodland and Mediterranean scrub land
OL,20,Fhas been destroyed by wildfires.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
